query:
SELECT id, sectionId, questionNumber, questionText, exampleEvidence, type 
FROM complianceQuestions 
WHERE type = 'serviceUser' 
ORDER BY sectionId, CAST(SUBSTRING_INDEX(questionNumber, '.', -1) AS UNSIGNED) 
LIMIT 5;
